        "text": "plus q factorial over 1 factorial,",
        "start": 410.24,
        "duration": 3.04
    },
    {
        "text": "plus q factorial over 2 factorial,",
        "start": 413.28,
        "duration": 3.12
    },
    {
        "text": "plus q factorial over q",
        "start": 416.4,
        "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
        "text": "factorial - because I've eventually",
        "start": 419.68,
        "duration": 1.68
    },
    {
        "text": "reached the qth term - but then",
        "start": 421.36,
        "duration": 2.08
    },
    {
        "text": "there's a whole series of other terms",
        "start": 423.44,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "which- for now let's just call them",
        "start": 425.44,
        "duration": 1.84
    },
    {
        "text": "the rest, right? There's- there'll be a q",
        "start": 427.28,
        "duration": 2.08
    },
    {
        "text": "factorial over q plus 1 factorial, and a",
        "start": 429.36,
        "duration": 2.64
    },
    {
        "text": "q factorial of a q plus \n2 factorial - it just",
        "start": 432.0,
        "duration": 2.08
    },
    {
        "text": "goes on forever.",
        "start": 434.08,
        "duration": 1.28
    },
    {
        "text": "But we've just- we know from our",
        "start": 435.36,
        "duration": 2.399
    },
    {
        "text": "assumption",
        "start": 437.759,
        "duration": 0.961
    },
    {
        "text": "that e equals p over q,",
        "start": 438.72,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "okay? And that then means that",
        "start": 442.08,
        "duration": 3.2
    },
    {
        "text": "q factorial times e,",
        "start": 445.28,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": "this is equal to - what is that equal to?",
        "start": 448.72,
        "duration": 2.56
    },
    {
        "text": "That's equal to q minus 1 factorial,",
        "start": 451.28,
        "duration": 2.8
    },
    {
        "text": "times q, times e - because that's what q",
        "start": 454.08,
        "duration": 2.64
    },
    {
        "text": "factorial is, it's q minus 1 factorial",
        "start": 456.72,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "times q.",
        "start": 458.72,
        "duration": 1.44
    },
    {
        "text": "But we all- we already know that q times",
        "start": 460.16,
        "duration": 2.4
    },
    {
        "text": "e equals p,",
        "start": 462.56,
        "duration": 2.16
    },
    {
        "text": "so this is just q minus 1 factorial",
        "start": 464.72,
        "duration": 4.08
    },
    {
        "text": "times p.",
        "start": 468.8,
        "duration": 1.36
    },
    {
        "text": "So this is an integer, that's the key",
        "start": 473.199,
        "duration": 2.641
    },
    {
        "text": "point here.",
        "start": 475.84,
        "duration": 0.88
    },
    {
        "text": "q minus 1 factorial is just an integer, p",
        "start": 476.72,
        "duration": 2.24
    },
    {
        "text": "is just an integer, so the product of",
        "start": 478.96,
        "duration": 1.44
    },
    {
        "text": "them is just an integer. So q factorial",
        "start": 480.4,
        "duration": 2.079
    },
    {
        "text": "times e, the left hand side of this",
        "start": 482.479,
        "duration": 1.681
    },
    {
        "text": "expression,",
        "start": 484.16,
        "duration": 1.12
    },
    {
        "text": "is an integer, okay? Now let me look at",
        "start": 485.28,
        "duration": 3.199
    },
    {
        "text": "the right hand side of this expression.",
        "start": 488.479,
        "duration": 1.84
    },
    {
        "text": "Well hopefully you can be convinced that",
        "start": 490.319,
        "duration": 3.201
    },
    {
        "text": "this thing that",
        "start": 493.52,
        "duration": 0.959
    },
    {
        "text": "I've under- underlined here, this is also",
        "start": 494.479,
        "duration": 2.321
    },
    {
        "text": "an integer; q factorial is just an",
        "start": 496.8,
        "duration": 1.679
    },
    {
        "text": "integer,",
        "start": 498.479,
        "duration": 0.801
    },
    {
        "text": "this is q factorial over 1, well that's",
        "start": 499.28,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "just an integer,",
        "start": 501.28,
        "duration": 1.12
    },
    {
        "text": "this is q factorial over 2 factor-",
        "start": 502.4,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "factorial where the 2s cancel.",
        "start": 504.4,
        "duration": 1.84
    },
    {
        "text": "So this here is also an integer. This is",
        "start": 506.24,
        "duration": 2.16
    },
    {
        "text": "an integer,",
        "start": 508.4,
        "duration": 0.96
    },
    {
        "text": "this is an integer; this then implies",
        "start": 509.36,
        "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
        "text": "that the rest",
        "start": 512.24,
        "duration": 1.2
    },
    {
        "text": "must be an integer, right? I can't have an",
        "start": 513.44,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "integer here,",
        "start": 515.44,
        "duration": 1.12
    },
    {
        "text": "an integer here, and have this not being",
        "start": 516.56,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "an integer. Otherwise it would- imagine\nthis",
        "start": 518.56,
        "duration": 2.399
    },
    {
        "text": "was a half, then I'd have an integer",
        "start": 520.959,
        "duration": 2.801
    },
    {
        "text": "equals an integer plus a half and that's",
        "start": 523.76,
        "duration": 1.6
    },
    {
        "text": "not right. So so the rest must be an\ninteger.",
        "start": 525.36,
        "duration": 2.56
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, so now I'm going to concentrate on",
        "start": 527.92,
        "duration": 2.32
    },
    {
        "text": "the rest,",
        "start": 530.24,
        "duration": 0.88
    },
    {
        "text": "right, so what is the rest?",
        "start": 531.12,
        "duration": 3.04
    },
    {
        "text": "Well we also have that the rest,",
        "start": 534.16,
        "duration": 3.52
    },
    {
        "text": "let me call it r, right,",
        "start": 537.68,
        "duration": 3.12
    },
    {
        "text": "for the rest, what is it? \nIt's q factorial,",
        "start": 540.8,
        "duration": 4.159
    },
    {
        "text": "because that's what I multiplied",
        "start": 544.959,
        "duration": 1.281
    },
    {
        "text": "everything by, into-",
        "start": 546.24,
        "duration": 2.08
    },
    {
        "text": "and it's all these other expressions. So",
        "start": 548.32,
        "duration": 2.079
    },
    {
        "text": "it's",
        "start": 550.399,
        "duration": 1.12
    },
    {
        "text": "1 over q plus 1 factorial,",
        "start": 551.519,
        "duration": 4.161
    },
    {
        "text": "plus 1 over q plus 2 factorial,",
        "start": 555.68,
        "duration": 4.8
    },
    {
        "text": "plus - well let me do \nthe next one - q plus",
        "start": 560.48,
        "duration": 3.039
    },
    {
        "text": "3 factorial, and it goes on forever",
        "start": 563.519,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "and ever",
        "start": 565.519,
        "duration": 1.121
    },
    {
        "text": "like this, okay? I can now divide out,",
        "start": 566.64,
        "duration": 2.8
    },
    {
        "text": "because,",
        "start": 569.44,
        "duration": 0.72
    },
    {
        "text": "you know, this- imagine q was 6:",
