        "duration": 1.44
    },
    {
        "text": "1 over 7, that would be all that's left.",
        "start": 577.12,
        "duration": 2.399
    },
    {
        "text": "So this is just",
        "start": 579.519,
        "duration": 1.121
    },
    {
        "text": "equal to 1 over q plus 1,",
        "start": 580.64,
        "duration": 3.92
    },
    {
        "text": "plus 1 over- and this is 1 over q plus 1",
        "start": 584.56,
        "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
        "text": "times 1 over q plus 2, and this",
