        "duration": 3.279
    },
    {
        "text": "is just you - get the \nidea - 1 over q plus 1",
        "start": 591.839,
        "duration": 3.841
    },
    {
        "text": "times 1 over q plus 2 times 1 over q",
        "start": 595.68,
        "duration": 3.04
    },
    {
        "text": "plus 3,",
        "start": 598.72,
        "duration": 1.6
    },
    {
        "text": "plus dot dot, okay.",
        "start": 600.32,
        "duration": 3.04
    },
    {
        "text": "And what I can do, I can simplify this.",
