        "duration": 3.041
    },
    {
        "text": "forever and ever and ever.",
        "start": 622.88,
        "duration": 1.28
    },
    {
        "text": "So the key point now that I want to make",
        "start": 624.16,
        "duration": 2.239
    },
    {
        "text": "is that this- this is what the rest is,",
        "start": 626.399,
        "duration": 1.761
    },
    {
        "text": "it's exactly this,",
        "start": 628.16,
        "duration": 1.52
    },
    {
        "text": "but the the proof- the the key thing of",
        "start": 629.68,
        "duration": 3.2
    },
    {
        "text": "the proof now comes in the fact that I",
        "start": 632.88,
        "duration": 1.6
    },
    {
        "text": "know that this",
        "start": 634.48,
        "duration": 1.2
    },
    {
        "text": "has to be less than the following: well I",
        "start": 635.68,
        "duration": 3.279
    },
    {
        "text": "keep the 1 over q plus one,",
        "start": 638.959,
        "duration": 2.401
    },
    {
        "text": "I keep the 1. Now 1 over q plus 2",
        "start": 641.36,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": "is less than 1 over q plus 1 right?",
        "start": 644.8,
        "duration": 2.8
