    {
        "text": "Imagine q was 6 again, then 1 over 8",
        "start": 647.6,
        "duration": 4.4
    },
    {
        "text": "is less than 1 over 7. Similarly here",
        "start": 652.0,
        "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
        "text": "this is less than 1 over q plus 1",
        "start": 655.6,
        "duration": 3.52
    },
    {
        "text": "squared, right? Because this would be 1",
        "start": 659.12,
        "duration": 2.64
    },
    {
        "text": "over 8 times 1 over 9,",
        "start": 661.76,
        "duration": 1.92
    },
    {
        "text": "which is clearly less than 1 over 7",
        "start": 663.68,
        "duration": 2.159
    },
    {
        "text": "squared.",
        "start": 665.839,
        "duration": 0.881
    },
    {
        "text": "And it just goes on like that, right, that",
        "start": 666.72,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "this is less than this.",
        "start": 668.72,
        "duration": 1.84
    },
    {
        "text": "Now this number here is less than 1,",
        "start": 670.56,
        "duration": 3.68
    },
    {
        "text": "because q is- q is going to be bigger",
        "start": 674.24,
        "duration": 1.839
    },
    {
        "text": "than 1, this is less than 1.",
        "start": 676.079,
        "duration": 2.481
    },
    {
        "text": "There is a- there's a beautiful little",
        "start": 678.56,
        "duration": 1.68
    },
    {
        "text": "proof due to Gauss,",
        "start": 680.24,
        "duration": 2.08
    },
    {
        "text": "and I'm going to prove it for you so",
        "start": 682.32,
        "duration": 1.519
    },
    {
        "text": "that we can then just finish this off.",
        "start": 683.839,
        "duration": 2.161
    },
    {
        "text": "Gauss apparently did this when he was",
        "start": 686.0,
        "duration": 1.279
    },
    {
        "text": "about three right? All right so",
        "start": 687.279,
        "duration": 2.641
    },
    {
        "text": "so there's the following: if x,",
        "start": 689.92,
        "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
        "text": "some number, is less than 1 then we",
        "start": 693.92,
        "duration": 2.32
    },
    {
        "text": "have the sum",
        "start": 696.24,
        "duration": 0.88
    },
    {
        "text": "of n terms which is 1 plus x",
        "start": 697.12,
        "duration": 4.159
    },
    {
        "text": "plus x squared plus x cubed",
        "start": 701.279,
        "duration": 3.201
    },
    {
        "text": "plus..up to x to the n. You can see what's",
        "start": 704.48,
        "duration": 3.359
    },
    {
        "text": "going to happen right? My x's are going",
        "start": 707.839,
        "duration": 1.601
    },
    {
        "text": "to be my 1 over q",
        "start": 709.44,
        "duration": 1.12
    },
    {
        "text": "plus 1s, because these will be the",
        "start": 710.56,
        "duration": 2.079
    },
    {
        "text": "things that's less than 1, that's where-",
        "start": 712.639,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Now let me do the following: Gauss did",
        "start": 714.639,
        "duration": 1.521
    },
    {
        "text": "this.",
        "start": 716.16,
        "duration": 1.679
    },
    {
        "text": "x times that, right, is equal",
        "start": 717.839,
        "duration": 3.041
    },
    {
        "text": "to - and then it becomes I multiply the",
        "start": 720.88,
        "duration": 2.32
    },
    {
        "text": "1, I get",
        "start": 723.2,
        "duration": 0.8
    },
    {
        "text": "the x, I get the x squared, I get the x",
